# Add the sample name at the top
sed -i '1s/^/genes s20170005 s20170011 s20170012 s20170020 s20170021 s20170022 s20170027 s20170030 s20170034 s20170038 s20170039 s20170042 s20170054 s20170055 s20170056 s20170058 s20170059 s20170060 s20170065 s20170067 s20170096 s20170098 s20170103 s20170104 s20170108 s20170110 s20170113 s20170117 s20170119 s20170120 s20170133 s20170134 s20170135 W10 W11 W5 W6 W7 W9 s20170105 s20170032 s20170033 s20170035 s20170036 s20170037 s20170045 s20170046 s20170047 s20170048 s20170051 s20170052 s20170053 s20170057 s20170007 s20170076 s20170077 s20170078 s20170081 s20170123 s20170124 s20170125 s20170126 s20170127 s20170128 s20170129 s20170130 s20170132 \n /' merge2.txt 
